Titolo: Minerva (video game)

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Minerva is an episodic series of single-player modifications ("mods") for Valve's Half-Life 2. The mod was created by Adam Foster. Installments are released as each is finalized: the three releases for the Metastasis chapter have already been made, with the third installment released on October 1, 2007.
The plot and settings of Minerva are linked to Someplace Else, Foster's original map for Half-Life, and to Half-Life 2 itself.
The mod was released on Steam on April 30, 2013.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
